sentences.english: The finite element analysis (FEA) and the variable density methods were used. The optimization method and process were presented.
sentences.chinese: 采用有限元法与变密度法，给出了优化方法和步骤。

sentences.english: Analysis is made on wave propagation in soils under high speed train loads by two-dimensional finite element method.
sentences.chinese: 基于有限元法分析了地铁运行引起的土的波动特性。

sentences.english: The Transfer Matrix Method (TMM) and the Finite Element Method (FEM) are two ordinary calculating methods for rotary system.
sentences.chinese: 传递矩阵法和有限元法是转子动力学分析的常用方法。

sentences.english: The last, A strength evaluation of the big gear ring was obtained by the theory of the finite element analysis .
sentences.chinese: 最后应用有限元计算理论给出了大齿圈的强度评价。

sentences.english: In this paper the finite element method is applied to analyze the web stress state of WCW I beam when it is straightened.
sentences.chinese: 本文利用有限元法分析了矫直时腹板的应力状态。

sentences.english: Finite element analysis is adopted to calculate secondary quench exchanger tube sheet of ethylene plant.
sentences.chinese: 对乙烯装置第二急冷锅炉的管板进行了有限元分析。

sentences.english: MSC/NASTRAN is a general finite element analysis software.
sentences.chinese: NASTRAN是一种通用的有限元结构分析软件。

sentences.english: A two-dimensional axisymmetric finite element model of sampling tube and sediments is built.
sentences.chinese: 建立了取样管与沉积物接触的二维轴对称有限元模型。

sentences.english: The Quasi-Conforming Element (QCE) technique is introduced in this paper for calculating the penalty-finite element problems.
sentences.chinese: 本文将拟协调元方法应用于罚函数有限元中。

sentences.english: Using finite element analysis software MSC.
The 3-D finite element model is built for the modal analysis of board-level package.
sentences.chinese: 建立了板级封装的三维有限元模型并进行模态分析。

sentences.english: First the model is subdivided into simple meshes that are orientable and manifold.
sentences.chinese: 有限元模型首先分解成一系列的可定向的流形模型。

sentences.english: The up-to-date research progress of the finite element analysis of soil cutting is reviewed.
sentences.chinese: 阐述了用有限元法分析土壤切削问题的研究进展情况。

sentences.english: The rational FEM formulation, which is quite different from the usual FEM formulation, is proposed here.
sentences.chinese: 提出了与常现有限元迥然不同的理性有限元列式。

sentences.english: The rational FEM formulation, which is quite different from the usual FEM formulation, is proposed here.
sentences.chinese: 提出了与常现有限元迥然不同的理性有限元列式。

sentences.english: The rigid plastic finite method is applied to deal with the new power spinning process of the counter roller spinning.
sentences.chinese: 针对对轮旋压新工艺进行了刚塑性有限元分析。
